query:
INSERT INTO gp_access_tokens (gamePresenterId, token, isActive, createdAt)
SELECT id, 'AgnesSuvorov_Test_Token_2026', 1, NOW()
FROM game_presenters WHERE name LIKE '%Agnes Suvorov%'
LIMIT 1;
